text: The Baojun Yunhai is a compact Crossover SUV made by SAIC-GM-Wuling under the Baojun brand since 2024. == History and Features == The Baojun Yunhai was shown in May 2024.https://carnewschina.com/2024/05/12/baojun-yunhai-5-seater- suv-official-images-unveiled-in-china/ and was put on sale in September 2024..https://carnewschina.com/2024/09/11/saic-gm-wuling-launched-baojun- yunhai-suv-for-15450-usd-in-china/ it has the brand's new design language and the SUV has both Plug-in hybrid and electric versions the Plug-in hybrid version combines a 1.5 liter petrol engine with a electric motor with a E-CVT transmission while the electric version has a electric motor of 150 kW (201 hp) and a range of 500-600 km (311-373 mi). == Markets == The Baojun Yunhai was first released on the Chinese market and is expected to be sold in other countries. == References == Category:Chinese automobiles Category:2020s automobiles Category:Sport utility vehicles
